      "The proposal is to use clusters, graphs and networks as models in order to analyse the Web structure.",
      "Clusters, Graphs, and Networks for Analysing Internet-Web-Supported Communication within a Virtual Community",
      "The Internet can be thought of as a social network, where users interact with each other and form relationships based on their shared interests or activities.",
      "Clustering is a method for grouping objects in such a way that objects within each cluster are more similar to each other than they are to objects outside the cluster.",
      "A virtual community is a group of people who share common interests or goals and interact with each other online, often through social media platforms or forums.",
      "Clusters provide knowledge representation and organization."
